	* src/simage_quicktime.c:
	x86 support:

	GraphicsExportGetDefaultFileNameExtension() returns a big-endian
	four-charaacter code => need to swap, or else we'll believe we have
	support for GNP images but not PNG...
	[4867bbd7d9af]

