	* ChangeLog.sh:
	Ignore changes in cfg/m4/ (renamed from conf-macros).
	[54c410ecd5c0]

2000-10-20  Morten Eriksen  <mortene@sim.no>

	* configure, configure.in:
	Fixed a typo; let the library name depend on the
	SIMAGE_MAJOR_VERSION, not be hardcoded to "simage0.dll" on
	MSWindows. :^/
	[87728e9eb31d]

