	[69cdd49c42cd]

2000-10-19  Morten Eriksen  <mortene@sim.no>

	* msvccc:
	Moved cl.exe wrapper script to conf-macros module.
	[ed2b8ca95b27]

	* include/simage.h.in, src/simage.c:
	Provide a function simage_free_image() to avoid Windows going
	bananas when we free() in the application code.
	[cda51a6c517e]

	* tests/loaders.c, tests/loaders.cpp:
	Testcode was supposed to be a C file.
	[38b7f95e7503]

	* simage-config.in:
	Added --build option.
	[8d89efb38e2b]

	* src/Makefile.am, src/Makefile.in:
	The .dll must be built by its installation name, as the name is also
	coded into the file itself (very clever, those Microsoft engineers).
	[767528a6ae42]

	* msvccc:
	Handle conversion of -L properly. Also simplified dereferencing of
	symlinks.
	[541d2105d608]

	* Makefile.in, config.h.in, configure, configure.in, include/simage.h,
	include/simage.h.in, include/stamp-h2.in, src/Makefile.am,
	src/Makefile.in, src/simage.c, stamp-h1.in:
	The configure process will now set up SIMAGE_*_VERSION defines in
	simage.h.

	Also added a new function simage_version() to the API and renamed
	simage_add|remove_plugin_loader() to the shorter
	simage_add|remove_loader().
	[ef2695c2c9cb]

	* src/Makefile.am, src/Makefile.in:
